{"tid":912684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男遇癡漢「被拉手摸他GG」　自拍照曝光網友驚呆了","createTime":"2018-11-23T01:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T07:29:52.000Z","uid":32511,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"019e556e511d91fbc69faa6b6f36c2d99477a0bd","tid":912684,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mxtdjx6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxtdjx6.png&h=37ca643a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3VSz6s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3VSz6s.png&h=a81bd50a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zADXMc8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzADXMc8.png&h=d9fa5461&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XKxhMc9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXKxhMc9.png&h=3a4cbe35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本一位男網友穿女裝外出，結果遇到電車痴漢，他把這段恐怖經歷PO上網，並且附上自己的自拍照，讓看到的網友驚呆了。<br />\n <br />\n日本網友在《5CH》討論區發文指出，他穿女裝搭電車的時候遇到癡漢，並說明當時上車的人很多，他被擠上車後，後面就有一名癡漢把他的裙子拉起來，然後隨著電車的晃動揉他的屁股，隨後癡漢再拉他的手，往癡漢的GG摸去，遇到這樣的經歷，他立刻躲到到其他車廂避免被癡漢騷擾，等到下車後發現他的內褲上還沾有癡漢的體液。<br />\n <br />\n這樣的經歷讓網友很好奇他穿女裝到底如何，於是原PO分享自拍照後讓大家暴動「靠邀這看起來超可愛」、「這走在外面不會知道是男的吧」、「等級也太高」。原PO也說他身高170、體重55公斤，喜歡穿女裝，也把身體上大多數的毛用除毛膏處理掉了，這次遇到癡漢，還是第一次摸到其他人的GG。"},{"pid":"747998104257d33498433273a4a568d9cb87ab66","tid":912684,"uid":118710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c475b845cc49959950b4011fed610a365bfffc68","tid":912684,"uid":125623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:47:42.000Z","msg":"This is great"},{"pid":"ded24589ce17792db3d370a30e74503771e9f289","tid":912684,"uid":7877,"like":0,"di